<para id="fs-id1170572540874">In the following exercises, use the graph of the function <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>f</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math> shown here to find the values, if possible. Estimate when necessary.</para>
